---
// 暂时把 getCollection 删掉，排除数据源报错导致的 404
const title = "Life Fragments";
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <style>
        body { background: #EEC43E; margin: 0; font-family: serif; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; min-height: 100vh; }
        nav { width: 100%; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid black; background: white; }
        .feed { max-width: 600px; width: 90%; margin: 50px 0; }
        .post { background: white; border: 3px solid black; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 40px; box-shadow: 10px 10px 0px black; }
        .post img { width: 100%; border: 1px solid #eee; }
        .post-text { margin-top: 15px; line-height: 1.6; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav><a href="/">← 返回首页 BACK TO HOME</a></nav>

    <div class="feed">
        <h1 style="font-size: 50px;">LIFE</h1>
        
        <article class="post">
            <img src="https://picsum.photos/600/600" />
            <div class="post-text">
                <p><b>2026.03.24</b></p>
                <p>如果看到这个页面，说明路径终于通了！这是我的第一条生活碎片。</p>
            </div>
        </article>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
